{"tid":1997004,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以前嘅我太天真","createTime":"2020-05-01T10:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T15:59:33.000Z","uid":351252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b2d235ec696dd9df427d5bae0c17524350c88122","tid":1997004,"uid":351252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:41:29.000Z","msg":"明明就想理性討論件事，講返自己嘅觀點，指出佢嘅觀點有咩謬誤，佢就發哂脾氣起哂槓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夾硬話我係教壞其他人，再屈我就係咁睇，<br />\n我冇講過嘅嘢就講到我有講過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係好驚呢啲咁閪嘅人<br />\n一唔同意見就起哂槓再屈鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我太天真<br />\n以為可以冷靜客觀表達自己睇法<br />\n互相交流<br />\n但我發現呢句世界就係有啲人佢唔要同你討論<br />\n就係要同你嘈交<br />\n發現自己理虧都係繼續屌你屈你<br />\n就係唔回應你嘅觀點<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我對住呢啲人真係想大巴一巴摑柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但咁做都係冇用<br />\n我再講落去都只係繼續聽佢講閪嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f8ab32a02633653a51092d8ea85a7ae41fc50e","tid":1997004,"uid":67296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T15:25:08.000Z","msg":"襯放假出去行下，睇少陣連登會冇咁激氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf2d9c1880327a75b9eea1043c1680d42aa34e3","tid":1997004,"uid":351252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78f8ab32a02633653a51092d8ea85a7ae41fc50e","tid":1997004,"uid":67296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T15:25:08.000Z","msg":"襯放假出去行下，睇少陣連登會冇咁激氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T15:59:33.000Z","msg":"出咗去成日睇下大自然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舒服返曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}